txt.en: Umbar Baharbêl, the City of the Corsairs, has been known by many names and inhabited by many peoples through the history of Middle-earth. In the aftermath of the War of the Ring, freed of the Heirs of Castamir and the Great Southern Empire of Ordâkh, the citizens of Umbar now seek for better fortunes, whether it be by their own hands or under the governance of the Kindred of the Coins.
